s:8829:"<p>首先有一台电脑安装 VMware Workstation Pro 安装教程自行百度。<br>参考<br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/698351524">Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS安装</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_25599925/article/details/121491373">第一章 运维必备技能：安装Ubuntu 24.04操作系统</a><br><a href="https://github.com/coolsnowwolf/lede/tree/master">Lean 的 LEDE 源码仓库</a><br><a href="https://openwrt.org/docs/guide-developer/toolchain/install-buildsystem">openwrt构建系统设置</a><br>这里使用 <a href="https://releases.ubuntu.com/22.04/ubuntu-22.04.5-live-server-amd64.iso">Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS</a> 服务器版<br>打开VMware Workstation Pro</p><h1 id="cl-1"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#cl-1"></a>Ubuntu Server 22.04 安装</h1><p>在 VMware Workstation新建虚拟机，按下面步骤安装即可；<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3056113469.jpg" alt="1.jpg" title="1.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1086229772.jpg" alt="02.jpg" title="02.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/4114935436.jpg" alt="03.jpg" title="03.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1475614508.jpg" alt="04.jpg" title="04.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2855872974.jpg" alt="05.jpg" title="05.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1591555911.jpg" alt="06.jpg" title="06.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/489283864.jpg" alt="07.jpg" title="07.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1709653815.jpg" alt="08.jpg" title="08.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1963752676.jpg" alt="09.jpg" title="09.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2261972709.jpg" alt="10.jpg" title="10.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/253142548.jpg" alt="11.jpg" title="11.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2684641661.jpg" alt="12.jpg" title="12.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/500133306.jpg" alt="13.jpg" title="13.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/600560288.jpg" alt="14.jpg" title="14.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2952890505.jpg" alt="15.jpg" title="15.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3990212764.jpg" alt="16.jpg" title="16.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2896341613.jpg" alt="17.jpg" title="17.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3985836650.jpg" alt="18.jpg" title="18.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/216580852.jpg" alt="19.jpg" title="19.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2362242200.jpg" alt="20.jpg" title="20.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2045738536.jpg" alt="21.jpg" title="21.jpg"><br>这里设置静态ipv4地址方便后续管理<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1523870609.jpg" alt="22.jpg" title="22.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1426872899.jpg" alt="23.jpg" title="23.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/4073727640.jpg" alt="24.jpg" title="24.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3087811452.jpg" alt="25.jpg" title="25.jpg"><br>这里可以设置代理，不用下一个<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/651037707.jpg" alt="26.jpg" title="26.jpg"><br>这里设置软件源<a href="https://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu">https://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu</a><br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/456584809.jpg" alt="27.jpg" title="27.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1301778181.jpg" alt="28.jpg" title="28.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3455215750.jpg" alt="29.jpg" title="29.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2353130233.jpg" alt="30.jpg" title="30.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2463490549.jpg" alt="31.jpg" title="31.jpg"><br>这里设置在“Profile configuration（配置文件配置）”界面，设置“Your name（你的名字）”：请自行设置，这里设置为“raymond”，设置“Your server’s name（你的服务器名字）”：请自行设置，这里设置为“ubuntu2204”，设置“Pick a username（择用户名）”：请自行设置，这里设置为“raymond”，设置“Choose a password（选择一个密码）”：请自行设置，设置“confirm your password（确认你的密码）”：请重新输入刚才输入的密码，然后选择“Done”，回车进行下一步<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/437073971.jpeg" alt="32.jpeg" title="32.jpeg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3692594760.jpg" alt="33.jpg" title="33.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/4007327797.jpg" alt="34.jpg" title="34.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/539474067.jpg" alt="35.jpg" title="35.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/4166409106.jpg" alt="36.jpg" title="36.jpg">至此Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS操作系统开始安装，安装完毕重启虚拟机。<img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2205501182.jpg" alt="37.jpg" title="37.jpg">使用你自己创建账号登录Ubuntu,设置root密码(默认未设置);<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2366173758.jpg" alt="38.jpg" title="38.jpg">使用命令sduo passwd root设置root密码，如下：<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2191425672.jpg" alt="39.jpg" title="39.jpg">注：$ 普通用户 # root用户 使用su root验证是否正常切换到root用户，如下：<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2636217709.jpg" alt="40.jpg" title="40.jpg">设置SSh,通过root账号，编辑ssh服务配置文件，默认情况Ubuntu不允许终端使用root账号ssh链接服务器的<br>使用vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config命令，修改ssh_config文件中下图中2处位置配置文件信息；<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3367918899.jpg" alt="41.jpg" title="41.jpg">使用systemctl restart ssh重启ssh服务；<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1919121330.jpg" alt="42.jpg" title="42.jpg">使用MobaXterm终端软件验证测试ssh登录；<br><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2073645647.jpg" alt="43.jpg" title="43.jpg"><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/2727309075.jpg" alt="44.jpg" title="44.jpg">设置静态IP，如果前面未设置设置静态IP地址的，可以使用命令vim /etc/netplan/00-installer-config.yaml编辑网卡配置文件<img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/3110973925.jpg" alt="45.jpg" title="45.jpg">应用更改，运行命令 sudo netplan apply<img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/1350906179.jpg" alt="46.jpg" title="46.jpg"><br>换源</p><pre><code class="lang-shell">bash &lt;(curl -sSL https://linuxmirrors.cn/main.sh)</code></pre><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sorcererr/article/details/128675919">Ubuntu开启NTP时间同步</a></p><h1 id="cl-2"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#cl-2"></a>OpenWrt 系统准备前 建议自行准备梯子 上手有门槛</h1><p>这里使用<a href="https://github.com/coolsnowwolf/lede#">Lean 的 LEDE 源码</a><br>安装编译依赖</p><pre><code class="lang-shell">sudo apt update -y
sudo apt full-upgrade -y
sudo apt install -y ack antlr3 asciidoc autoconf automake autopoint binutils bison build-essential \
bzip2 ccache clang cmake cpio curl device-tree-compiler flex gawk gcc-multilib g++-multilib gettext \
genisoimage git gperf haveged help2man intltool libc6-dev-i386 libelf-dev libfuse-dev libglib2.0-dev \
libgmp3-dev libltdl-dev libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev libpython3-dev \
libreadline-dev libssl-dev libtool llvm lrzsz msmtp ninja-build p7zip p7zip-full patch pkgconf \
python3 python3-pyelftools python3-setuptools qemu-utils rsync scons squashfs-tools subversion \
swig texinfo uglifyjs upx-ucl unzip vim wget xmlto xxd zlib1g-dev</code></pre><pre><code class="lang-shell">sudo apt update
sudo apt install build-essential clang flex bison g++ gawk \
gcc-multilib g++-multilib gettext git libncurses5-dev libssl-dev \
python3-setuptools rsync swig unzip zlib1g-dev file wget</code></pre><p>下载源代码，更新 feeds 并选择配置 ，这里使用镜像站链接<br><a href="https://fcp7.com/github-mirror-daily-updates.html">2025年3月更新！18个Github镜像站，国内更快部署下载</a></p><pre><code class="lang-shell">git clone https://kkgithub.com/coolsnowwolf/lede
cd lede
./scripts/feeds update -a
./scripts/feeds install -a
make menuconfig</code></pre><p><img src="http://192.168.2.25/usr/uploads/2025/03/614916897.png" alt="menuconfig.png" title="menuconfig.png"><br>本期结束</p>";